BuildRequires:    R-CRAN-seqinr 
Requires:         R-CRAN-ape 
Requires:         R-CRAN-coxme 
Requires:         R-CRAN-doParallel 
Requires:         R-CRAN-dplyr 
Requires:         R-CRAN-foreach 
Requires:         R-CRAN-iterators 
